metadata.description:
The year is 2169. One hundred years ago a cataclysmic event known only as 'The Awakening' ruptured the delicate powers that kept the supernatural at bay.

As ethereal rifts opened across the globe, humans discovered they were wrong about heaven and hell. Neither good nor evil, they are simply worlds full of beings much like our own.

Hosts of angels and demons left the comforts and sorrows of their realms to join our own, to live alongside humankind.

Today, the lines between devils, angels, and men have blurred. New beings walk the earth, each with incredible stories and powers of their own.

This is the new world order.

This is Saints & Sinners.
